## Tech Stack

- **React 19** — UI components
- **TypeScript 5.9** — strict mode
- **Vite 8** — build tool with HMR
- **SVG** — all race visualization (no canvas or WebGL)
- **Mulberry32** — deterministic PRNG
- **Zero runtime dependencies** beyond React

